of Sendai Local History,’ Hobundo, 1979.* Tōshirō Shimizu, ‘Miyagi Prefecture General History,’ Shinyakusha Bookstore, 1931. Reprinted by Hobundo in 1976.* Sendai City History Compilation Committee, ‘Sendai City History,’ Special Edition 2 (Archaeological Materials), Sendai City, 1995. Articles on "Kabutozuka Kofun" and "Ōnodera Burial Mound Group" authored by Atsushi Fujisawa.== External Links ==* [http://www.city.sendai.jp/Category:kk]]]][[Category:/bunka/02.html Cultural Properties of Sendai] (Sendai City Board of Education)** [http://www.city.sendai.jp/kyouiku/bunkazai/iseki/c0000000036.html Kabutozuka Kofun]]][[Category:kk]]]][[Category:dd]]]][[Category:kk]]]][[Category:Kofun in Miyagi Prefecture]]]][[Category:kk]]]][[Category:dd]]]][[Category:kk]]]][[Category:History of Taihaku Ward]]]][[Category:kk]]]][[Category:dd]]]][[Category:kk]]]][[Category:Scallop-shaped keyhole tumuli]]]][[Category:kk]]]][[Category:dd]]]][[Category:kk]]]][[Category:Unsorted completion categories]]
